  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The millers saw the door of hell and screamed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The main organizer of the opposition, Samagi Jana Balawega, Kandy District Member of Parliament, lawyer Mr. Lakshman Kiriella, said, \"Maybe the millers are shouting lies today because they see the suffering of the people and see the suffering of the people.\"",
        "He also stated that what has been done so far is to exploit the innocent people of the country.",
        "He said that under the current circumstances, the date for leaving the country was unthinkable and as far as he knew, the loan from the International Monetary Fund would be around next December."
      ],
